{
  "addonId": "documentReaderForNvda",
  "displayName": "Document reader for NVDA",
  "URL": "https://github.com/blind-tech-nexus/document-reader-nvda-addon/releases/download/1.0/document-reader-1.0.nvda-addon",
  "description": "A powerful NVDA add-on for accessible document reading with advanced features.\n\nDeveloped by Sujan Rai, this add-on allows you to read your document files directly within the NVDA screen reader.\n\nOften, we need to read document files, but uploading them to external servers can compromise your privacy. This add-on ensures that your documents are processed entirely locally, keeping your documents safe.\n\nBeyond simple document reading, this add-on provides a wealth of features for manipulation, accessibility, OCR, read-aloud capabilities, and much more.\nSupported documents:\nPDF, docx, epub.\n\nThis add-on is the next generation add-on for the previous and outdated PDF reader add-on.\nFor feedback and support, email: blindtechvisionary@gmail.com\nJoin our official Telegram channel for more resources: https://t.me/blindtechvisionary\n\nMade and maintained in: Nepal.\n\nThank you for using this add-on!",
